<title>CHINA: Credit Lyonnais sets warrants on HSBC.</title>
<headline>Credit Lyonnais sets warrants on HSBC.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1997-07-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>Credit Lyonnais Financial Products (Guernsey) Ltd said on Friday it proposed to issue 39 million American-style call warrants on HSBC Holdings Plc.</p>
<p>Ten warrants control one share.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE     HK$300	 PREMIUM	  20.14 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE	HK$2.6792    GEARING	  10.15x</p>
<p> MATURITY	   07.MAY.98    PAYMENT DATE   04.AUG.97</p>
<p> LISTING	    HONG KONG    LISTING DATE   06.AUG.97</p>
<p> SPOT REFERENCE   HK$272	 BOARD LOT	4,000</p>
<p> NOTE		 CASH OR PHYSICAL DELIVERY OF STOCKS AT THE</p>
<p>			DISCRETION OF THE ISSUER.</p>
<p>-- Hong Kong newsroom (852) 2843 6370</p>
